# Files excluded from the EAS Build upload archive.
# Keeps the upload small and clean, and lets EAS prebuild the native projects
# fresh from app.json (CNG). Including android/ or the .expo web cache here was
# corrupting the project tarball (paths with '#', stale com.viibe.nightlife),
# which broke extraction on the build worker (PREPARE_PROJECT tar failure).

node_modules/
android/
ios/
.expo/
dist/
web-build/
*.log
.DS_Store
